'''Wallball''' was a sport played on a court. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] tried to get [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] to play it once. The Death Star's recreational facilities' sport courts were also configurable for playing wallball and other popular games.

The [[Luxury liner/Legends|luxury liner]] [[Kuari Princess/Legends|''Kuari Princess'']] included forty-five zero-[[Gravity/Legends|gee]] wallball courts across the [[Starship/Legends|starship]].<ref name="RPG">[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game (first edition)|''Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game'']]</ref>

